## ⬇️ Installation

### Installation of the CLI

#### Installation via [Cargo Binstall]

```bash
cargo binstall -y {{ package.name }}
```

<img width="100%" alt="Installation via cargo-binstall" src="{{ github.repository.link }}/raw/master/rust/etc/asciinema/install.gif"/>

#### Installation via [Cargo]

```bash
cargo install {{ package.name }} --locked --features=cli
```

### Installation of the Library

<details>
<summary>Installation from Crates.io</summary>

#### Installation from [Crates.io]

```bash
cargo add --dev {{ package.name }}
```
</details>

<details>
<summary>Configuration in <code>Cargo.toml</code></summary>

#### Configuration in `Cargo.toml`

Enable all default features:

```toml
[dev-dependencies]
{{ package.name }} = { version = "0" }
```

Enable only specific features:

```toml
[dev-dependencies]
{{ package.name }} = { version = "0", default-features = false, features = ["alloc"] }
```
</details>

